snippet.title: Screen Rant
snippet.description:
Screen Rant is one of the top entertainment authorities on YouTube, uploading daily videos and movie theories about Marvel, Avengers, Disney Pixar, Family Guy, The Simpsons, gaming and all things superhero! 

Screen Rant continues to be the go-to source for movie and TV facts, theories and behind the scenes knowledge!
